Welcome to FLANGO FIGHT!

In this action-packed adventure, you have three lives. Each time you collide with an enemy, you lose one life.
Your mission: Survive, defeat enemies, and unlock new levels!

Avoid enemy collisions to progress through the game and prove your skills.
Are you ready for the challenge?

Good luck and have fun!
Victory is yours🥳 But the journey isn’t over yet🎮.
Click Spacebar to throw bombs at the witch and dodge the witch spells to avoid death
